Planned extra credit:
- multithread server
- user auth
- interactive mode
- any file type
- change directory
- allow client to save file to arbitrary name

CONTROL CONNECTION
client sends "port\n"
client sends "command\n"

DATA CONNECTION
"ls"
    server sends "de\n" for each de
    server sends "\0\0\n"
"get"
    server sends "length\n"
    server sends "file" (1500 byte chunks)

